org.apache.hadoop.fs

Class TestLocalDirAllocator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.TestLocalDirAllocator

  • public class TestLocalDirAllocator
extends Object
    This test LocalDirAllocator works correctly; Every test case uses different buffer dirs to enforce the AllocatorPerContext initialization. This test does not run on Cygwin because under Cygwin a directory can be created in a read-only directory which breaks this test.
